<p>J. Bryan III used to challenge his friends to think of an English word that contains either of the following strings of letters:</p>
<p>ILIL</p>
<p>ILIW</p>
<p>&#8220;I&#8217;ve never played the game with anyone who could solve either of these combinations.&#8221; Can you?</p>

